Working with Naya Asha Family Clinic was so much fun. It has beautiful UI Design with simple and perfect color schemes. Although it doesn't have login system for customers, they can make online appointments. It has got Content Management System (CMS) where the clinic can view and interact with all the appointments. Moreover, they can add, update or delete their services, their doctors with their time schedules and their packages.

Naya Asha Family Clinic, associated with Naya Asha Health Co-operative Ltd., is an emerging clinic with 24 hours pharmacy services and free delivery services along with various quality health services including dental services, adult vaccinations, general body checkup, endoscopy, ultrasonography, ECG and so on.
